arStrings.szText: One night, Tavish came into the Goose screaming about a bear turning into a man, heh. Had Torben and me in stitches. “Druids!?”
Fondly recalling the past. "Heh" is a dry laugh. Nairne is gently mocking Tavish's silly ideas and voice when she imitates him by saying "Druids!?"
Said he’d find their den and bop each one 'til they proved him true.
